<div type="original">
<pb f="1r" n="1" xml:id="pb-orig-1r-1" facs="#zone-pb-1r-1"/><lb n="1" xml:id="l-1"/>
<ab>Mon cher ami</ab><lb n="2" xml:id="l-2"/>
<ab>Après avoir erré sur la côte, je me <lb n="3" xml:id="l-3"/>suis fixé à Cassis.<anchor n="1" xml:id="note-o-1"/> Je vous envoie mon <lb n="4" xml:id="l-4"/>adresse afin que vous me puissiez <lb n="5" xml:id="l-5"/>donner de vos bonnes nouvelles<c type="kp">_</c>– J’ai écrit <lb n="6" xml:id="l-6"/>à votre frère, il ne m’a point encore répondu<c type="kp">_</c>–<anchor n="2" xml:id="note-o-2"/></ab><lb n="7" xml:id="l-7"/>
<ab rend="indent">Je vous serre bien cordialement la main<c type="kp">_</c>–</ab>
<vg:whiteline/><lb n="8" xml:id="l-8"/>
<ab>Votre P. Signac</ab>
<vg:whiteline/><lb n="9" xml:id="l-9"/>
<ab>2 Place de la Republique – Cassis<c type="kp">_</c></ab>
    <vg:whiteline/><pb f="1v" n="2" xml:id="pb-orig-1v-2" facs="#zone-pb-1v-2"/></div>
<div type="translation">
<pb f="1r" n="1" xml:id="pb-trans-1r-1" facs="#zone-pb-1r-1"/>
<ab>My dear friend,</ab>
<ab>After wandering along the coast, I’ve settled in Cassis.<anchor n="1" xml:id="note-t-1"/> I’m sending you my address so that you can give me good news about yourself. I’ve written to your brother, he hasn’t replied to me yet.<anchor n="2" xml:id="note-t-2"/></ab>
<ab rend="indent">I shake your hand most cordially.</ab>
<vg:whiteline/>
<ab>Your <rs type="pers" key="1350">P. Signac</rs></ab>
    <vg:whiteline/>
    <ab>2 place de la République – Cassis.</ab><pb f="1v" n="2" xml:id="pb-trans-1v-2" facs="#zone-pb-1v-2"/></div>
<div type="notes">
<note n="1" xml:id="n-1" target="#note-t-1">
<ab>On his way from Paris to the South, <rs type="pers" key="1350">Signac</rs> had visited Van Gogh on 23 and 24 March (<ref target="let752.xml">see letter 752</ref>). Cassis is south-east of Marseille, on the Mediterranean Sea.</ab></note>
<note n="2" xml:id="n-2" target="#note-t-2">
<ab>For <rs type="pers" key="1350">Signac</rs>’s letter to Theo, <ref target="let752.xml#n-1">see letter 752, n. 1.</ref></ab></note></div></body></text></TEI>
